<body>
    <h1>Download FitPals Android Project</h1>
    <p>Click the button below to download the complete Android Studio project:</p>
    
    <a href="fitpals.zip" class="download-button" download>Download FitPals Project (ZIP)</a>
    
    <div class="instructions">
        <h2>Installation Instructions:</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Download the ZIP file using the button above</li>
